{"tid":1552980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用數字解釋你地聽點解要爆黨鐵同跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T17:48:54.000Z","uid":14921,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0e82a5e776be1f685d05559697e98debc7488142","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"唔知邊到傳話黨鐵好大收入係商埸/物業<br />\n但係睇返佢annual report, 數字說明一切<br />\n<br />\nAs at 31 Dec 2018,<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2TeSLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2TeSLy.png&h=cf2422e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黨鐵2018年度報告就睇到, 「香港客運業務收入」係指車務收入,即係你地平時搭車啊<br />\n而客運業務收入佔據整體收入係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接近一半</span></span> (19,490/53,930)<br />\n而車站租務加埋商埸租務收入加埋先係11billion (6,458+5,055), 遠遠不及19billion<br />\n至於「中國內地及國際......收入」, 呢個係咩呢, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGUhQU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGUhQU1.png&h=c55f87fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實呢個係海外幫手營運, 實際代返入黨鐵褲袋其實唔多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以其實你地平時搭車既錢係佢地主要收入來源,<br />\n其次先係租金收入</span></span><br />\n唔好以為自己搭程車先十幾蚊<br />\n但係365日咁多人搭就好大舊錢<br />\n數字俾你睇到講緊一年有差唔多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二百億</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好啦講完數字,<br />\n想你地明白黨鐵已經係我地敵人,<br />\n我地一定要予以懲罰<br />\n懲罰行動包括但不在此限：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本人絕不建議長者卡</span></span><br />\n雖然你只係用$2去搭, 但係黨鐵係報告上都係收正價, 因為你俾$2, 政府俾餘額<br />\n咁當然罷買黨鐵商埸都一樣要做啦<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊做衰黨鐵今年下半年條數,<br />\n雖然佢地最大股東係政府,<br />\n但係佢地都要同其他股民交代<br />\n從而向黨鐵高層施加壓力"},{"pid":"f301471162f36a923976ada654061f95cf0ad8a2","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"從今開始<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵各站, 隨時都會受到應有懲罰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提, 圍站長係無意思,<br />\n我寧願你把握圍站長時間去做實際啲嘅嘢"},{"pid":"6bbc6a5ca12d1a5707b4af720aa033ca41b501bc","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:52:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f198ea1ccb279920df4c5270c3f285ee9613197","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定<br />\n不過要快"},{"pid":"e81096b45dac4858a6f261be2f01e18a538413a3","tid":1552980,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cba6d6c7229c07b37bbe61192cd92aaa20d0ed82","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"提供合理性"},{"pid":"d859eb6474807f8e8c5c1341917d6f10562e1f5f","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"解釋你地聽點解要咁做"},{"pid":"bcd535b5f1a096e1325a9ae6fa0273b0924e0d54","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e2d256880c7eaecc001b198c43a86a89a6a68bf","tid":1552980,"uid":231007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6d2d4b0d3a2a3f3f3c807435ea35bbde548594c","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c77bd2c29296bfbad7dc6ef1078d23b1d3fb0066","tid":1552980,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16ec681ca8cd55b6bd573991decea94b544d5bd7","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"263e183d5d330fc0cdea74017f5a507162a16d3f","tid":1552980,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c77bd2c29296bfbad7dc6ef1078d23b1d3fb0066","tid"