0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:15.000Z","msg":"黨鐵食屎狗"},{"pid":"15d5d50ac3facc05ac3f2f7d8e3bf903e432fbc6","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62bf65ac90bd6e7c347e6dc575bf97005dc05d47","tid":1552980,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"大致認同<br />\n但想講$2飛都無問題<br />\n損唔到人咪利下己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d758aeaa4e8b84569cef4b5f37f8434363989ef2","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"食屎啦黨鐵"},{"pid":"047fee4d69bdb5b6d5e6a285738925d67b6c5080","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"清算黨鐵"},{"pid":"a037b1d5905f5e570e5ad4dbdb7b4fa478ea9c6d","tid":1552980,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"大學站直情唔洗跳 有個空位係閘同閘中間 就咁行出去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2751041d9a46c07cfa520f365cf94cb4b190fa98","tid":1552980,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8503fba0e99675a9f57c70702063f946cf1834ad","tid":1552980,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a037b1d5905f5e570e5ad4dbdb7b4fa478ea9c6d","tid":1552980,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"大學站直情唔洗跳 有個空位係閘同閘中間 就咁行出去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"邊鼠啊 點解我唔知嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d95e6d2eb272edbcd60cf6b34bc401c0a00752","tid":1552980,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e82a5e776be1f685d05559697e98debc7488142","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"唔知邊到傳話黨鐵好大收入係商埸/物業<br />\n但係睇返佢annual report, 數字說明一切<br />\n<br />\nAs at 31 Dec 2018,<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2TeSLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2TeSLy.png&h=cf2422e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黨鐵2018年度報告就睇到, 「香港客運業務收入」係指車務收入,即係你地平時搭車啊<br />\n而客運業務收入佔據整體收入係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接近一半</span></span> (19,490/53,930)<br />\n而車站租務加埋商埸租務收入加埋先係11billion (6,458+5,055), 遠遠不及19billion<br />\n至於「中國內地及國際......收入」, 呢個係咩呢, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGUhQU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGUhQU1.png&h=c55f87fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實呢個係海外幫手營運, 實際代返入黨鐵褲袋其實唔多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以其實你地平時搭車既錢係佢地主要收入來源,<br />\n其次先係租金收入</span></span><br />\n唔好以為自己搭程車先十幾蚊<br />\n但係365日咁多人搭就好大舊錢<br />\n數字俾你睇到講緊一年有差唔多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二百億</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好啦講完數字,<br />\n想你地明白黨鐵已經係我地敵人,<br />\n我地一定要予以懲罰<br />\n懲罰行動包括但不在此限：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本人絕不建議長者卡</span></span><br />\n雖然你只係用$2去搭, 但係黨鐵係報告上都係收正價, 因為你俾$2, 政府俾餘額<br />\n咁當然罷買黨鐵商埸都一樣要做啦<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊做衰黨鐵今年下半年條數,<br />\n雖然佢地最大股東係政府,<br />\n但係佢地都要同其他股民交代<br />\n從而向黨鐵高層施加壓力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b07c56e0839ef390938cb212cc0acf9a754633e","tid":1552980,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f301471162f36a923976ada654061f95cf0ad8a2","tid":1552980,"uid":14921,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"從今開始<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵各站, 隨時都會受到應有懲罰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提, 圍站長係無意思,<br />\n我寧願你把握圍站長時間去做實際啲嘅嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"支持快閃 不被捕"},{"pid":"78365665da8ad827a9e9808acf7502f070211975","tid":1552980,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"我唔撚搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24c49806fa4b9a301a3542add49a446638353ae","tid":1552980,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8503fba0e99675a9f57c70702063f946cf1834ad","tid":1552980,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a037b1d5905f5e570e5ad4dbdb7b4fa478ea9c6d","tid":1552980,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"大學站直情唔洗跳 有個空位係閘同閘中間 就咁行出去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"邊鼠啊 點解我唔知嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"巴士站果邊 有個鐵欄封左 但有位行出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7b1d7a4f2aa35387a5f4cb3e0d119a274c6d6b","tid":1552980,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24c49806fa4b9a301a3542add49a446638353ae","tid":1552980,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8503fba0e99675a9f57c70702063f946cf1834ad","tid":1552980,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a037b1d5905f5e570e5ad4dbdb7b4fa478ea9c6d","tid":1552980,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"大學站直情唔洗跳 有個空位係閘同閘中間 就咁行出去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"邊鼠啊 點解我唔知嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"巴士站果邊 有個鐵欄封左 但有位行出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"